{"tid":1810970,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"道歉啟事","createTime":"2020-01-04T10:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T18:17:11.000Z","uid":116322,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2b9641287be8b1164c3b8df8de048659edd07b","tid":1810970,"uid":116322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFmkYwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFmkYwf.jpg&h=8cfc23a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有讀者講《漂亮鄰居的夜半剁肉聲》同狩獵夢的人《每晚望門孔，都見到隔離屋條女企門外對我詭異咁笑》好似，我睇完即刻向夢巴解釋同道歉，夢巴好好人，傾向相信我無心。先澄清：我絕非刻意，好可能係我睇過大綱／個故但過咗年幾唔記得睇過。但係似就係似、錯要企定，浪費大家寶貴時間，我橘子綠茶在此衷心向狩獵夢的人再次道歉、誠心向一眾讀者道歉。<br />\n<br />\nLink只供查閱，請支持實體書(書名《墮樂園》)<br />\n《每晚望門孔，都見到隔離屋條女企門外對我詭異咁笑》連載日期：19-03-2018<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/598448\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/598448</a><br />\n《漂亮鄰居的夜半剁肉聲》連載日期：27-12-2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799697\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799697</a>"},{"pid":"f172736f955662d0f3866080842f954d66c60d8f","tid":1810970,"uid":233665,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"以為係為左爛尾道歉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecdb4d20310bf2de6f7aa1d4afb9ec316b9390b","tid":1810970,"uid":88663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"懂不懂道歉？"},{"pid":"15c8969e8a7ce0f5a379d7cbbfa577e4c6d239e7","tid":1810970,"uid":316590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767cb37dd5dca3b2cbeb4b9a7f1a7c5fa7a6bc66","tid":1810970,"uid":308676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996fe029ca4c0e9050f046f522ae31aab9867350","tid":1810970,"uid":319045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"